387
00:21:12,561 --> 00:21:15,461
Or at least cases about them, right?

388
00:21:15,461 --> 00:21:17,161
Of course.

389
00:21:17,161 --> 00:21:20,161
Yoko Okino asked me to work for her several times.

390
00:21:20,161 --> 00:21:22,461
What? You mean that top idol?

391
00:21:22,461 --> 00:21:24,061
You're indeed a renown detective, aren't you?

392
00:21:24,061 --> 00:21:25,361
I guess so.

393
00:21:25,361 --> 00:21:29,361
