00:22:05,161 --> 00:22:07,061
It seems that Conan's tired.

404
00:22:07,061 --> 00:22:08,661
Okay.

405
00:22:09,861 --> 00:22:11,661
No doubt about it.

406
00:22:11,661 --> 00:22:15,361
There was someone recently, too.

407
00:22:15,361 --> 00:22:16,761
Let's see...

408
00:22:16,761 --> 00:22:19,561
You know, they were on TV a lot,

409
00:22:19,561 --> 00:22:22,961
